*** Files of the Inspector ***

QUEUE-sig.aml		: Signature of a priority queue
MkQueue.aml		: Implementation

Prefs.aml		: Preferences of the Inspector.
AbsTree.aml		: Abstract trees (abstract view of displayed data)
TypeMappers.aml		: Mappings from types to abstract trees.
BasicTypeMappers.aml	: Type-mappers for records and tuples
BuiltinTypeMappers.aml	: Type-mappers for builtin types (int, list, ...)
Cache.aml		: Given a type, finds its description
Common.aml		: Instruction of the virtual machine, tool functions
HANDLERS-sig.aml
MkHandlers.aml		: Handlers = actions of the graphical interface
MONITORS-sig.aml
PrintInfo.aml           : (For debug) Prints information about nodes.
MkMonitors.aml		: Monitors for futures and references
Inspector.aml		: Main entry of the Inspector
Test.aml		: Test the inspector


gui/
 BOARD-sig.aml
 MkBoard.aml		: The Board is the top-level view of the canvas
			  'inspect val' adds one entry in the board
 CANVAS_DRIVER-sig.aml
 MkCanvasDriver.aml	: Driver for the gnome-canvas
 GrTypes.aml		: Definition of graphical trees (concrete view)
 GR_TREE-sig.aml
 MkGrTree.aml		: Maps abstract trees to graphical trees
 LAYOUT-sig.aml
 MkLayout.aml		: Redo the layout of a tree (after an update)
 LAYOUT_LIST-sig.aml
 MkLayoutList.aml	: Update the layout of lists after an update
 MAIN_WINDOW-sig.aml
 MkMainWindow.aml	: Builds the main GUI-window
 MkAboutWindow.aml	: Builds the "about" window
 MkConnections.aml	: Connects widgets to handles
 MkPrefsWindow.aml	: Builds the preferences window
 SELECTION-sig.aml
 MkSelection.aml	: Manages the selections
 UPDATE-sig.aml
 MkUpdate.aml		: Dynamic update (futures and user interaction)
 MkTooltip              : Tooltips

